reviewText:
I recently viewd this splended piece of cinematography and while the story and the performance of Rusty Williams and Scott Scaresdale where in fact stellar, there was a moment of lackluster in the performance by Todd Taylor.

Todd Taylor, the smaller of the two doctors, making his first non-adult star performace comes off as cocky and weak. The former adult erotica man-on-man movie star known as "HOTBOD TODD" probably should have kept to money-shooting across the room; the only real skill he does best.

-EAD.
